'''二尖瓣閉鎖不全'''（{{lang|en|Mitral insufficiency}}，或{{lang|en|mitral regurgitation}}，簡稱'''MR'''或'''MI'''），是描述[[心臟|心臟]][[二尖瓣|二尖瓣]]在[[心室|心室]]收縮期間無法完全閉合的現象。此疾病會導致左心室的[[血液|血液]]經二尖瓣{{le|血行逆流|Regurgitation (circulation)|逆流}}至左心房內<ref>[http://www.mountsinai.org/Other/Diseases/Mitral%20valve%20regurgitation Mitral valve regurgitation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mountsinai.org/Other/Diseases/Mitral%20valve%20regurgitation |date=20100105064418 }} at {{tsl|en|Mount Sinai Hospital, New York||Mount Sinai Hospital}}</ref>。本疾病為最常見的{{tsl|en|valvular heart disease|瓣膜性心臟病}}<ref name='MedlineMitChron2008'>{{cite encyclopedia |last=Weinrauch |first=LA |encyclopedia=Medline Plus Encyclopedia |title=Mitral regurgitation - chronic |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000176.htm |accessdate=2009-12-04 |edition= |date=2008-05-12 |publisher=U.S. National Library of Medicine and National Institutes of Health |volume= |location= |id= |doi= |pages= |quote= |archive-date=2016-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705053440/https://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000176.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
